{"title":"雄师百万挽狂澜——“七一”参加十三陵水库落成典礼书怀","authors":["郭沫若"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄师百万挽狂澜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“七一”参加十三陵水库落成典礼书怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭沫若"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄师百万挽狂澜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五载工程五月完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此十三陵畔路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四山环水水环山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横流壁立锁蛟龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百丈高堤气势雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已见西风今压倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间万代颂东风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磴道千层入谷深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要将黄壤变黄金。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温榆河水怀乡土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸上山山已植林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果树万株种满缠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼苗千石殖深渊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南风物眼前是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琼岛芳亭系钓船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（五）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水停立使电光来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜群星落九垓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征服自然为我用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一环开定万环开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（六）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只今双喜大临门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七一佳期水库存。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献礼及时人山海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千声万岁震乾坤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（七）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾万马走惊雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换骨群生已脱胎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂止保持唯水土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还从建库建人才。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（八）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科技文工大有人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪炉炼罢换金身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神生产将逾昔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造终当日日新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1958年7月1日）（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭老在水库工地上　本报记者　吕相友摄"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1}